    public class EnumComboBox<T extends Enum<T>>
extends ComboBox<T>
implements AutoBuildAware
    ComboBox that chooses an Enum value.

    When instances are created by FieldBuilder, the setEnumClass(java.lang.Class<T>) method will be configured automatically using the return type of the annotated getter method (this happens via onAutoBuild(java.lang.Object, java.lang.reflect.Method, java.lang.annotation.Annotation)).
